/======================================================= Observations =======================================================/

1. ArithmeticException - Occurs when / by zero.
2. NumberFormatException - Occurs when input give is String instead of int.
3. ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException - Occurs when no input found
4. NullPointerException  - Occurs when string input = null (string.length()).
5. We cant use .equal() with int primitive datatype.
6. int canâ€™t be null; only reference types (like Integer) can.
    ex: int a = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);
